{"tid":581822,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無啦啦抑鬱","createTime":"2018-03-05T16:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T17:53:50.000Z","uid":55156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"afc6441c321c3f58fb62eb1f27b5a1819cb1cef9","tid":581822,"uid":55156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"唔想見人，好驚同人接觸+眼神接觸，見人就驚，朋友都係，唔敢開口講野，好自卑覺得自己係零，一世都唔會有人愛，因為人地根本唔會睇得上我<br />\n<br />\n平時係平常人一個，但唔知做咩會有一段時間係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知見到有人嘅地方，想永遠縮埋一角，覺得自己唔死都無用，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0295877761f3cb85cb73159d9f250038553ef18","tid":581822,"uid":167389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:04:42.000Z","msg":"咁個個嘅情緒都會有起有跌嘅。唔需要太介懷，做啲自己開心嘅事通常會舒服啲"},{"pid":"9baf5ee9d29867e91b953d08037b9771ae5c3016","tid":581822,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4927ebb9f61e1b2025a9e265e7c2f89431e8cca","tid":581822,"uid":3438,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T16:07:26.000Z","msg":"抑鬱係無啦啦㗎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882f06d3848f3f8b381b3abff3b579285e705eae","tid":581822,"uid":174829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T17:53:50.000Z","msg":"入嚟傾下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DuQpJFJHHWWQhEPmz12BoQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDuQpJFJHHWWQhEPmz12BoQ&d=9WSmceSPMME4aK%2F%2FDjvC4IzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=4819e565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DuQpJFJHHWWQhEPmz12BoQ</a>"}]}